Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:06.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:08.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:17.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:26.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:30.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:35.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.65,0:00:41.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.78,0:00:48.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:53.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:55.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:01:03.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.43,0:01:12.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:16.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:21.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:28.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:34.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:39.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:41.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.67,0:01:45.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.01,0:01:49.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:50.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.68,0:01:52.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:54.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:55.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.73,0:01:57.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:59.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:00.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:01.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:05.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:08.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:14.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:19.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:21.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:25.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:32.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.91,0:02:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hot Water"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Catch!\N--That was too high!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like a Rainbow Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get right on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'd like to give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.43,0:02:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:03:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe this resort was\Njust outside the Florian Triangle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am honored that you \Nare enjoying yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.26,0:03:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spa Island has twelve heated pools.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.82,0:03:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're lovely!\N--There are three lazy rivers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and a pool dedicated to diving.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We also have waterfalls for\Nmeditation and fifty baths,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,including a cola bath and a milk bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.94,0:03:25.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Milk Bath"\N"Women" "Men"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.90,0:03:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, we have water ping pong
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.53,0:03:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a floating casino for those\Nwho would like to play games.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.41,0:03:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can enjoy exquisite cuisine prepared\Nby master chefs at several restaurants.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As your host, nothing could make me happier
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.12,0:03:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,than to melt away the fatigue\Nfrom your long voyage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some lucky visitors may even get to\Nsee a circular rainbow and candy rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.88,0:03:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, aren't circular rainbows
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a rare natural phenomenon \Ncalled the "ocean's treasure"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.89,0:03:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've heard there hasn't\Nbeen a sighting in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.64,0:04:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I said, "some lucky \Nvisitors" may see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We might see some candy rain in just a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.02,0:04:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you jest!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it must be difficult\Nto run a resort on these waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since our opening, we've earned\N10 billion Berries a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're endorsed by the World Government,\Nso we haven't run into any problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our security is rock solid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm confident that our
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,regular guests have nothing to \Nfear as they kick back and relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.05,0:04:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10 billion Berries a year?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, that applies to pirates as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.68,0:04:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry if that spoiled your mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're a paying customer,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.65,0:04:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you're a pirate or\Npart of the Revolutionary Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:05:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are rather similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10 billion Berries! Berry, Berry, Berry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Slow-Slow Menace!\N'Silver Fox' Foxy Returns!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.91,0:05:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boo-yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Whoopee!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are those things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Candy! It's raining candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:06:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Candy ball raindrops!\NAnd they're only raining here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're super lucky! Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Candy too heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.59,0:06:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the ocean raccoon dog, Nukki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can transform into anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.05,0:06:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that this girl is called Rina.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:07:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The raccoon dog talked!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.53,0:07:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a raccoon dog! I'm a reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Eh?" Be nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want my lunch? But it's not a pirate lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.15,0:07:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Luffy, the man who will\Nbecome King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the ship doctor, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Captain Usopp, the sniper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! I didn't know there were\Nfunny pirates like you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! Now to chow do--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot about my big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:08:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis Sayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.73,0:08:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're eating up a storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy will eat anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ocean raccoon dogs are omnivores.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think he'll eat this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.16,0:08:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.97,0:08:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! He can transform into anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A babe! Please transform\Ninto the hottest babe ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, if only I was better with words!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:09:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Transform into Nami-san!\NPlease turn into Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.08,0:09:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're puny!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a stinking idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if you're puny,\NNami-san is still Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Aren't they goofy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.27,0:09:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.05,0:09:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the feast!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Thank you for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a blast! Thank you, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw! Is the ocean raccoon dog leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.81,0:10:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's who you'll miss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.88,0:10:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking for you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.51,0:10:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting old!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.91,0:10:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect you to get this far.\NYour drive is impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to catch you here and now,\Nbut that'll have to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've run into some rather familiar faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're doomed now that\NI've run into you, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't know who I am...\NHe doesn't remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.34,0:10:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Boss! Don't let it get to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By any chance, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the guy that Zoro and Sanji beat up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's doing it on purpose!\NIt has to be intentional!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:11:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Straw Hat, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.06,0:11:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tarnished my undefeated legacy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:05.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fox"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and stole our pride--our Jolly Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.86,0:11:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that you've forgotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.18,0:11:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Now I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.14,0:11:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Split-Head Fox!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.06,0:11:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm "Silver Fox" Foxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, be careful. As I recall,\Nhe can shoot a weird beam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, he isn't much of a threat\Nif we know what's up his sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't expect me to rely\Non the same tricks forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.72,0:11:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High-Speed Rotation Mirror Ball Amplifier!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.33,0:11:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thousand-Armed Kannon, Slow-Slow Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Shoot!\N--That's against the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:12:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn... it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... told... you... so!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything struck by my beam is\Nslow for thirty seconds afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.26,0:12:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.47,0:12:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now do you remember me, Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll start to fall in ten seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.92,0:12:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a lovely bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.53,0:12:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It made my skin so smooth. It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:13:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm a skeleton, so I don't have any skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.23,0:13:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky! Brook! Beat them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weapons Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cien Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I owe ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone okay? Gosh, you scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm a rubber man. I won't\Nlet that Slip-Head defeat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:14:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! You've added new\Nmembers to your crew, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Boss, they have a skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.14,0:14:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! Let's try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Victory is mine as long as \NI have this mirror ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! What are you doing?\NShut the door already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I'll get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please remain calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hot Water"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is everyone leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to ask you two something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about that notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.69,0:15:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foxy and his goons are after it, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foxy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.43,0:15:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pirates from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, we have a history with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.02,0:15:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'd say they were more\Ninterested in your notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.50,0:15:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I called it, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This notebook explains how to create jewels!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.41,0:15:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How to create jewels?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.66,0:16:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Rina!\N--It's okay. Leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that they're pirates, but they\Nseem trustworthy. Plus they're strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we try to deal with this on our own,\Nwe may never reach our goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, this notebook \Nbelonged to our father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.89,0:16:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow! It's full of numbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our father is an inventor, and those\Nformulas explain how to make jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can read this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis Sayo can. It goes right over my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You're something else, Sayo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about this? He included \Na nautical chart...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has a hot water mark and an "X."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's his secret message.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We think it's a hint regarding \Nhow to make jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? This?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:17:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The formula for making\Nthem is about 99% complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.05,0:17:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he hid the remaining 1% in this clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could the hot water mark \Nmean a hot springs...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In which case, the "X" might mean Spa Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. We reached the same\Nconclusion and snuck aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.33,0:17:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.53,0:17:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But despite all of our searching,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.07,0:17:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can't find anything to indicate\Nwe're on the right track.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt that notebook alone could\Ntell you how to make jewels...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.62,0:17:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Foxy Crew has come this\Nfar in pursuit of that notebook!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.14,0:17:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be legit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way you can make jewels!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.61,0:17:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father is a stupid liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is really stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.42,0:18:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rina and Sayo's Village\N-Three Years Ago-"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.40,0:18:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayo! Rina! This is horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a golden beetle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Legend says that our village\Nwill perish when one appears!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?! What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.37,0:18:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The paint is coming off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He fell for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.03,0:18:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scram!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.57,0:18:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.16,0:18:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief! Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.06,0:18:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, isn't this great? \NThe village isn't doomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:19:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it wonderful that it was a prank?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our father loved our village.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.12,0:19:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He loved it because that was\Nwhere our mother was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.88,0:19:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My research can save the entire village.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone will be able to live in comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.53,0:19:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What type of research \Nare you conducting, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jewels! How to create jewels!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.61,0:19:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jewels...? Those aren't\Nsomething you make, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.27,0:19:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad sounds neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:20:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't the least bit neat!\NHe's a horrible father!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years ago, he went on a journey\Nfor his research and never came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.11,0:20:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He abandoned us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been just the two of us ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've had to grit our teeth\Nas everyone made fun of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I don't have a dad. He's dead!"\NThat's what I've told myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.56,0:20:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then a month ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nukki suddenly came back\Nwith this notebook in his mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a letter in the notebook.\NWhat do you think it said?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dear daughters.\NPlease complete my research."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.20,0:20:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you believe him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was so busy with his research that\Nhe forgot about us for three years!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:21:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why must we risk our lives and\Ntravel to these dangerous waters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.35,0:21:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's stupid! Stupid!\NI don't believe a word he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.92,0:21:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fudging over his lies about\Nthe jewels with this picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.19,0:21:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he give us this quiz at the end?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad really is neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.84,0:21:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.38,0:21:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see those jewels.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.42,0:21:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you pay attention to a word I said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.42,0:21:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.11,0:21:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.62,0:21:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But didn't you come to \Nsearch for the treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.39,0:21:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't--my sister did!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.66,0:21:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm her bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.66,0:21:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her bodyguard?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister was insistent\Nabout searching for the secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I came to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.11,0:21:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.78,0:22:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am certain that there \Nis a way to make jewels!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.35,0:22:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.52,0:22:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis Sayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.17,0:22:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please help--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis Sayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.12,0:22:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got the girl. If you want\Nher back, do as I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.67,0:22:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doran?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.94,0:22:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.45,0:22:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship's host.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.69,0:22:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.17,0:22:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to uncover the secret\Nbehind that notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.89,0:22:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return the girl in \Nexchange for the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! Foxy wasn't our only enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.33,0:23:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.47,0:23:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Rina! Finish the research.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.38,0:23:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let Dad's dream fall\Ninto the hands of that jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.59,0:23:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad's research was nothing but lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.23,0:23:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t believe Sayo got caught\Nbecause of his notebook!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.53,0:23:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Luffy! Save Sayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.35,0:23:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.73,0:23:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Great Scramble for Treasure!\NCollapse! Spa Island!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.40,0:23:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
